    <div class="card">
        <h2>🔍 Key Insights</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Binders, Paper and Furnishings were among the most profitable products.</li>
            <li>November, December and September generated the highest sales volume.</li>
            <li>Orders without discounts achieved better profitability.</li>
            <li>Top customers generated a significant portion of total sales.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h2>💡 Business Recommendations</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Reduce unnecessary discounts.</li>
            <li>Increase marketing activities during peak sales months.</li>
            <li>Focus on highly profitable products.</li>
            <li>Improve performance in low-performing states.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

